WEBVTT

00:00:00.670 --> 00:00:04.250
-el Koblents. KAUNAS, LITVA.

00:00:05.230 --> 00:00:13.776
 mir hobn ir getrogn, un dortn grade iz geven azoy oyf a barg-aroyf aroyftsugeyn mit ir. mir zeen fun vaytns forn mashines un me balaykht di veg.

00:00:14.052 --> 00:00:18.830
⟨hobn mir⟩ farshtanen az me fort, ⟨m'hot shoyn⟩ gehert a shiseray, hot men glaykh genumen shikn

00:00:18.830 --> 00:00:20.779
hilf fun andere garnizonen.

00:00:21.122 --> 00:00:24.710
vos iz undz geblibn tsum ton? mir hobn fun ir tsugenumen dem AVTOMAT,

00:00:24.953 --> 00:00:29.925
fun ir aruntergenumen di, d- di shtivl, vayle undz iz geven ⟨z- g-⟩ groyse zakh,

00:00:29.998 --> 00:00:33.570
un mir hobn ir ar- avekgeleygt in zayt un mir zaynen antlofn

00:00:33.762 --> 00:00:35.050
tsum UNK.

00:00:35.050 --> 00:00:36.219
nu, mir zaynen gekumen

00:00:36.276 --> 00:00:39.378
tsum komandir, tsu Tseykon. mir hobn im gezogt

00:00:39.378 --> 00:00:43.180
az me hot ir dershosn un zi ligt dortn un dortn.

00:00:43.228 --> 00:00:46.327
un me hot ir ibergelozn, un azoy mir zaynen avek vayter.

00:00:46.857 --> 00:00:49.190
a- dos iz alts geyendik ts- oyf Lite.

00:00:49.354 --> 00:00:50.664
oyf Kazlove-Rude?

00:00:50.340 --> 00:00:51.890
oyf Kazlove-Rude, ye.

00:00:52.965 --> 00:00:57.397
un, v- i- vu hot ir zikh getrofn mit di regulere sovyetishe teyln?

00:00:58.213 --> 00:01:01.211
mit di regulere sovyetishe teyln? in Kazlove-Rude zayendik?

00:01:01.183 --> 00:01:09.091
neyn, dortn hobn mir shoyn zey nit gezen, di, di, di, rusishe teyln. dos iz geven nor dortn vu, nit vayt fun undzer baze. dortn hobn mir zikh mit zey getrofn.

00:01:09.199 --> 00:01:11.319
do zaynen mir shoyn gegangen on zey.

00:01:11.646 --> 00:01:12.855
ya, un i-...

00:01:12.034 --> 00:01:15.620
oyf Kazlove-Rude zaynen mir shoyn gegangen zelbshtendik.

00:01:15.375 --> 00:01:19.182
un az ir hot shoyn ongekumen in di velder fun Kazlove-Rude, vos hot ir dortn geton?

00:01:19.932 --> 00:01:23.959
mir, dortn hobn mir shoyn keyn, ni- nit gehat opgeshtelt zikh. mir zaynen shoyn gegangen oyf Kovne.

00:01:24.150 --> 00:01:26.776
fun Kazlove-Rude hot ir zikh shoyn farkirevet oyf Kovne?

00:01:26.180 --> 00:01:28.264
oyf Kovne, ye. dortn,

00:01:28.264 --> 00:01:37.459
mir hobn ge- mir hobn dortn gefunen, geven, dortn iz geven kontik oykh tsu partizaner, tsu s'iz dortn UNK; mir hobn gefunen zeyer fil untererdishe shtiblekh geven gemakht

00:01:37.465 --> 00:01:39.366
in Kazlove-Ruder velder.

00:01:39.507 --> 00:01:41.690
nu, dos hobn mir ⟨n-⟩...

00:01:41.970 --> 00:01:45.401
mir hobn getrofn ⟨ge- f-⟩ mir hobn getrofn etlekhe yidn

00:01:45.401 --> 00:01:48.714
vos zaynen, vos hobn ⟨ge-⟩ arumgeblondzhet in di velder.

00:01:48.940 --> 00:01:51.864
mir hobn zey gebetn, ⟨zey zoln zikh⟩ tsu undz tsu- tsueynikn,

00:01:51.864 --> 00:01:53.790
⟨hobn zey zikh⟩ nit gevelt.

00:01:54.627 --> 00:01:57.270
ir gedenkt, vi ir zayt arayn in Kovne?

00:01:57.428 --> 00:01:58.820
kh'gedenk zeyer gut.

00:01:59.368 --> 00:02:03.460
mir zaynen ongekumen durkh, Aleksot

00:02:03.604 --> 00:02:04.948
zaynen mir ongekumen.

00:02:05.697 --> 00:02:07.918
mir zaynen gekumen baym brik.

00:02:08.059 --> 00:02:10.601
der brik iz geven tse- oyfgerisn.

00:02:11.113 --> 00:02:14.490
gestro- gestroyet hobn soldatn a PONTONem brik.

00:02:14.067 --> 00:02:15.428
geboyt, yo?

00:02:14.902 --> 00:02:16.000
geboyt, ye.

00:02:16.125 --> 00:02:18.734
iber dem PONTONem brik zaynen mir ariber.

00:02:19.382 --> 00:02:21.772
nu, mir zaynen ariber oyf dem zayt un ⟨z-⟩

00:02:21.930 --> 00:02:25.147
nu, mir zaynen arayn in Kovne. Kovne iz geven zeyer pust.

00:02:25.407 --> 00:02:28.415
tsehakt UNK di shoybn UNK oyf LAISVES.

00:02:28.415 --> 00:02:31.424
getrofn undz epes a por yidn vos kh'hob zey nit gekont.

00:02:34.418 --> 00:02:37.440
nu, gekumen in Kovne...,

00:02:38.113 --> 00:02:44.975
hot men undz, dem gantsn OTRYAD, undz, az mir hobn zikh opgeshtelt oyf GRIUNVALDO gas, dortn geven, dortn hobn mir zikh opgeshtelt ale,

00:02:47.192 --> 00:02:48.654
un dortn

00:02:48.964 --> 00:02:51.641
hot men genumen sortirn

00:02:52.052 --> 00:02:55.360
di partizaner, vu me darf geyn arbetn.

00:02:55.984 --> 00:03:01.510
m'hot geshikt eynem in turme far a NADZIRATEL', a tsveytn UNK...

00:03:00.338 --> 00:03:02.306
far a oyfzeer, ya? oyfzeer.

00:03:02.177 --> 00:03:08.800
oyfzeer, ye. tsveytn oyfn b- ayznban-stantsye dortn in,...

00:03:09.653 --> 00:03:10.777
a vakh-man?

00:03:10.665 --> 00:03:13.110
vakh-man... UNK ongerufn.

00:03:13.110 --> 00:03:14.489
mir hot men bashtimt

00:03:14.698 --> 00:03:16.734
tsu arbetn in militsye.

00:03:17.871 --> 00:03:20.210
ikh hob gearbet in militsye in Kovne

00:03:20.352 --> 00:03:24.460
bay dray monat, ershte OTDELENye, oyf, oyf DAUKŠOS gas.

00:03:23.878 --> 00:03:25.357
ershte opteylung, ya?

00:03:24.730 --> 00:03:27.950
ershte opteylung, ye. oyf DAUKŠOS gas.

00:03:28.131 --> 00:03:31.804
nokh dem, az di armey hot zikh dernentert shoyn tsu Klaypede,

00:03:32.130 --> 00:03:36.700
hot men undz genumen, hot men gegebn a bafel, me zol otpravenen dortn fun Kovne,

00:03:36.700 --> 00:03:38.824
 n- naye kadern.

00:03:39.353 --> 00:03:42.429
hot men mir otpravet, mir un dortn nokh tsu mir iz geven.

00:03:42.429 --> 00:03:45.894
mir zaynen ongekumen nit vayt fun Klaypede in GARGŽDAI.

00:03:46.322 --> 00:03:51.159
dortn geven ⟨a-⟩ zeyer groyse kamfn. mir hobn gezen az me ken dortn nokh nit blaybn.

00:03:51.621 --> 00:03:55.150
zeyer f- etlekhe zaynen gekumen tsurik in Kovne,

00:03:55.182 --> 00:04:02.990
ober ikh un nokh zaynen dortn geblibn vartn biz,... s'flegn poshet svishtshenen di SNARYADn ibern kop hin un tsurik. azoy iz geven dortn,

00:04:01.982 --> 00:04:03.275
di koyln, ya?

00:04:03.011 --> 00:04:05.580
azelkhe, azelkhe BOY iz geven, azelkh-...

00:04:04.446 --> 00:04:06.110
azelkhene kamfn zaynеn ge-...

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:07.310
kamfn geven in Klaypede.

00:04:08.057 --> 00:04:10.329
nu, nokh dem, ⟨m'hot shoyn⟩ farnumen Klaypede,

00:04:10.774 --> 00:04:14.598
hot men undz otpravet, hot men undz a-, a- avekgeshikt arbetn in Shilute.

00:04:15.263 --> 00:04:17.889
Shilute bin ikh geblibn dortn arbetn.

00:04:18.029 --> 00:04:23.626
dortn hob ikh opgearbet fun fir un fertsiktn bizn tsvey un fuftsiktn yor.

00:04:23.565 --> 00:04:25.440
alts a milits-arbeter?

00:04:25.388 --> 00:04:28.301
mayn gantse, di gantse yorn, ken men zogn,

00:04:28.645 --> 00:04:33.480
⟨zaynen⟩ geven in vald mit di, mit di, mit di, litvishe...

00:04:32.948 --> 00:04:34.190
banditn.

00:04:33.480 --> 00:04:34.630
banditn, ye.

00:04:34.838 --> 00:04:36.941
bizn tsvey un fuftsiktn yor.

00:04:37.048 --> 00:04:40.496
yedn nakht, yedn nakht fleg zayn TREVOGes,

00:04:40.496 --> 00:04:42.570
TREVOGes. fleg men geyn ⟨PRICHЁS-⟩...

00:04:41.014 --> 00:04:42.459
me flegt aykh oyfheybn...

00:04:42.570 --> 00:04:45.470
vi, nu, durkh, di vald durkh-...

00:04:44.288 --> 00:04:45.429
durkhkamen.

00:04:45.470 --> 00:04:46.390
?

00:04:45.503 --> 00:04:46.611
durkhkamen.

00:04:46.390 --> 00:04:47.930
durkhkamen di vald, ye.

00:04:47.528 --> 00:04:50.711
ir flegt oykhet, onteyl nemen in o- in azelkhene operatsyes?

00:04:50.532 --> 00:04:51.532
ale mol.

00:04:51.477 --> 00:04:55.048
un s'flegt aykh oyskumen zikh durkhshisn mit, mit di ⟨va-⟩...?

00:04:54.379 --> 00:04:55.419
s'fleg zayn.

00:04:55.780 --> 00:04:57.574
eyn mol hobn mir,...

00:04:57.574 --> 00:05:00.532
zey flegn zikh azoy farmaskirn, di banditn...

00:05:00.673 --> 00:05:04.497
mir hobn eyn mol getrofn, a boym shteyt, a trukener boym.

00:05:05.095 --> 00:05:08.130
nu, geyt tsu eyner, zogt er,

00:05:08.267 --> 00:05:15.200
"⟨me darf do⟩ a kuk gebn" UNK er git a shtup der boym un der boym falt anider. untn iz geven a bunker untern boym gemakht

00:05:15.200 --> 00:05:17.998
dortn, un grade iz geven dortn iz geven di banditn.

00:05:18.291 --> 00:05:22.170
nu, m'hot zey glaykh bafeln, zey zoln aroysgeyn;

00:05:22.813 --> 00:05:27.931
anit ⟨veln⟩ UNK dershisn. a por zaynen aroys, oyfgehoybn di hent, opgegebn di gever, un andere

00:05:27.931 --> 00:05:32.040
zaynen nit aroys, hot men zey bavorfn mit granatn un zey zaynen dortn geharget gevorn ale.

00:05:31.858 --> 00:05:33.944
dos iz geven UNK bay tog tsu bay nakht?

00:05:34.153 --> 00:05:37.790
dos iz geven bay tog. mir flegn geyn bay tog UNK in di velder.

00:05:37.950 --> 00:05:47.010
mir hobn zeyer fil erter gefunen in hayzer. fleg zayn doplte vent gemakht, far m- nu, malines far, far di banditn.

00:05:46.658 --> 00:05:48.322
un ir flegt dos oysgefinen?

00:05:48.042 --> 00:05:49.369
oysgefinen, ye.

00:05:49.864 --> 00:05:51.649
eyn mol zaynen mir gegangen,

00:05:51.649 --> 00:05:58.970
 oykhet, m'hot undz gemoldn az in dem dorf gefint zikh, gefint zikh a grupe fun partizaner, fun di banditn.

00:05:58.369 --> 00:05:59.780
fun di litvishe, yo?

00:05:59.270 --> 00:06:00.760
fun di litvishe, ye.

00:06:01.238 --> 00:06:04.725
nu, zaynen mir avekgeforn, un mit undz iz geforn eyner a mayor.

00:06:04.731 --> 00:06:06.716
er iz durkhgegangen dem gantsn front.

00:06:07.043 --> 00:06:09.990
nu, hobn mir genumen geyn fun shtub tsu shtub zukhn dortn.

00:06:09.591 --> 00:06:10.850
in a dorf, ye?

00:06:10.430 --> 00:06:11.756
in a dorf, ye.

00:06:11.756 --> 00:06:16.220
nokh dem zaynen mir tsugegangen tsu a, tsu a SARAY. vi ruft men...

00:06:15.413 --> 00:06:16.453
a shayer.

00:06:16.220 --> 00:06:18.220
shayer. tsugegangen.

00:06:18.501 --> 00:06:23.034
nu, zogt men dortn, ho⟨t men⟩ im gezogt, "zay forzikhtik!"

00:06:23.597 --> 00:06:31.134
iz er tsugegangen, geefnt di tir. zogt er, "ha! ⟨ba," zogt er,⟩ "ikh bin durkhgegangen dem gantsn front. ikh bin UNK ⟨hot mir⟩ keyn zakh nit geshat. ⟨ikh'l nit⟩ do moyre hobn."

00:06:31.225 --> 00:06:35.520
vi nor er hot geefnt di, di tir, hot men im glaykh gegebn a otshered un er iz gefaln...

00:06:34.549 --> 00:06:36.602
a, a rey fun AVTOMAT, ye?

00:06:36.169 --> 00:06:40.450
ye. a rey fun AVTOMAT, un er iz glaykh gefaln bayn tir a toyter.

00:06:39.966 --> 00:06:41.478
un vos hot ir dan geton?

00:06:41.788 --> 00:06:49.200
nu, vos hobn mir gekent ton? UNK un dan, geyendik, di operatsye iz geven vider gemakht UNK in fir erter mit fir koyln-varfers,

00:06:49.200 --> 00:06:52.140
un m'hot alemen ⟨nokh dem, alemen⟩ oysge- oysgeharget⟨, vos...⟩

00:06:51.795 --> 00:06:55.805
un vi hot ir oysgeharget? ir zayt a- arayngerisn zikh, tsu ir hot farbrent dem shayer?

00:06:54.818 --> 00:06:55.818
⟨ha?⟩

00:06:55.818 --> 00:06:58.560
m'hot geefnt oyf im a fayer, oyf dem shayer,

00:06:58.560 --> 00:07:03.140
un er hot genumen brenen, ⟨un m'hot⟩ farvorfn mit granatn, un s'iz geendikt di operatsye geven.

00:07:02.747 --> 00:07:05.491
un keyner iz fun dortn ni- a lebediker nit aroys?

00:07:05.060 --> 00:07:07.660
mir flegn keyn lebedi⟨k-⟩ keynem nit aroyslozn.

00:07:08.704 --> 00:07:12.883
un vi hot ir aykh g- vi iz aykh gelungen avekgeyn fun der, milits?

00:07:12.750 --> 00:07:20.170
 fun der milits, ikh hob, ikh bin arayngefaln, vi me zogt, tsufelik;

00:07:20.170 --> 00:07:21.844
ikh bin dokh a shnayder fun fakh.

00:07:21.985 --> 00:07:25.525
kh'hob afile nit gevust mit vos m'est es, di mil- milits.

00:07:25.525 --> 00:07:27.379
m'hot mir bashtimt; ikh bin geven dan,

00:07:27.385 --> 00:07:33.100
 m'hot mir geshikt. vuhin m'hot mir geshikt, dortn bin ikh geforn. nu,

00:07:34.118 --> 00:07:39.470
ikh hob opgearbet in militsye dray, fir yor. kh'hob gezen az do iz far mir keyn ort nit.

00:07:40.142 --> 00:07:45.750
beshas ikh bin arayn in militsye hob ikh gedarft shraybn a, mayn gantse AVTOBIOGRAFye.

00:07:47.095 --> 00:07:50.565
hob ikh, gesh- hob ikh, nit geshribn...

00:07:50.723 --> 00:07:52.438
dan, far Stalin's tsaytn,

00:07:52.512 --> 00:07:57.680
der vos hot gehat a fraynt in oysland hot nit getort arbetn in di ORGANAKH.

00:07:58.198 --> 00:08:02.140
ikh hob nit, ikh hob nit gevust az ikh hob a bruder in Amerike.

00:08:03.565 --> 00:08:08.824
nu, un kh'hob nit geshribn, a- azoy az ikh bin geblibn arbetn. s'iz avekgegangen a dray, fir yor.

00:08:09.403 --> 00:08:14.210
mit a mol kumt on a briv fun bruder. er hot zikh dervust az ikh

00:08:14.517 --> 00:08:15.996
gefin zikh in Shilute.

00:08:16.288 --> 00:08:20.922
un di briv iz arayngefaln bayn dizhurner⟨... m'hot gezukht...⟩ bayn dizhurner,

00:08:20.963 --> 00:08:25.175
bay a leytenant eyner, un er hot di briv mir nit gornit gezogt, un er hot glaykh ibergegebn

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:27.830
in OTDEL KADROV dortn, vos, vu zey, vu zey...

00:08:26.515 --> 00:08:28.703
in kadern-opteylung, ye? ⟨fun⟩...

00:08:27.940 --> 00:08:30.720
ye, kader-opteylung. un,

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:32.937
un ikh hob nit gevust vegn di briv keyn zakh nit.

00:08:33.534 --> 00:08:37.570
ikh bin opgeven dortn, akht yor

00:08:37.570 --> 00:08:41.320
bin ikh geven a starshina. m'hot mir ⟨di,⟩ keyn ZVANye nit gegebn di gantse tsayt.

00:08:40.133 --> 00:08:43.063
keyn ofitserishe, madreyge hot ir nisht bakumen.

00:08:41.500 --> 00:08:46.890
gegebn, ye. in der tsayt, far der tsayt hobn andere shoyn gekrogn STARSHe leytenantn.

00:08:46.140 --> 00:08:48.125
ale zaynen shoyn gevorn leytenantn.

00:08:47.100 --> 00:08:50.210
ye. ⟨S- D-⟩ STA- DAZHE STARSHe leytenantn.

00:08:48.958 --> 00:08:51.044
afile eltere leytenantn.

00:08:50.890 --> 00:08:53.400
nu, un mir hot men di ZVANye nit gegebn.

00:08:53.582 --> 00:08:58.650
nokh dem iz gekumen tsu forn UNK geven in Klaypedsker ⟨KR-⟩,...

00:08:59.100 --> 00:09:01.690
geven ⟨regyo-⟩ nit keyn rayon, nit UNK...

00:09:00.484 --> 00:09:01.963
krayzn, mistome.

00:09:01.810 --> 00:09:03.740
 KRAY Klaypedsker...

00:09:02.712 --> 00:09:03.769
krayz!

00:09:03.740 --> 00:09:06.480
krayz Klaypedsker, hobn mir gehert tsu Klaypedsker krayz, ye.

00:09:04.652 --> 00:09:06.350
Klaypeder krayz, ya?

00:09:06.492 --> 00:09:08.983
gekumen tsu forn eyn mol der, a polkovnik

00:09:09.006 --> 00:09:11.328
fun, fun

00:09:11.335 --> 00:09:13.686
militsye, der natshalnik militsye.

00:09:13.686 --> 00:09:17.170
nu, s'iz geven a, a, a sobranye.

00:09:16.971 --> 00:09:18.129
a farzamlung.

00:09:17.460 --> 00:09:18.765
a farzamlung.

00:09:18.765 --> 00:09:23.158
un ikh hob zikh avekgeshtelt, kh'hob im gefregt, "vos, vos iz di P- vos iz di sibe?

00:09:23.485 --> 00:09:28.086
tsuzamen mit mir arbetn, hobn shoyn ZVANyes ⟨MLADSHe OFITSERSKe⟩, un mir git men nit.

00:09:28.395 --> 00:09:31.426
"nu," zogt er, "ikh'l dos aykh, ikh'l dos alts,"...

00:09:31.078 --> 00:09:32.354
makhn klor.

00:09:32.108 --> 00:09:33.317
"makhn klor."

00:09:33.508 --> 00:09:37.737
nokh dem iz geven, bay undz iz geven eyner fun, fun POLITCHAST' a yid.

00:09:38.014 --> 00:09:44.320
hot er zikh avekgeshtelt, zogt er, "ikh bin, ikh bin shoyn, ikh bin bakant mit, mit Koblents's DELO."

00:09:45.625 --> 00:09:47.990
nokh dem, er iz avekgeforn, der polkovnik.

00:09:47.990 --> 00:09:50.208
ruft er mir araynet, der,

00:09:50.653 --> 00:09:53.150
⟨ZAMPOPOLITCHAST'⟩, Mikhlis...

00:09:52.273 --> 00:09:55.406
der f-, f- part- fun politishe opteylung, ye?

00:09:54.629 --> 00:09:55.629
ye.

00:09:55.733 --> 00:09:56.976
UNK

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:57.870
familye zayne iz geven Mikhlis.

00:09:57.420 --> 00:09:58.393
a yid.

00:09:57.970 --> 00:09:58.832
a yid, ye.

00:09:59.833 --> 00:10:02.493
⟨nu,⟩ ruft er mir arayn. zogt er mir...

00:10:03.411 --> 00:10:06.310
er hot mir nit gezogt vegn di briv keyn zakh nit...

00:10:06.398 --> 00:10:10.970
zogt er, "du vest arbetn nokh tsvantsik yor, vest keyn ofitser nit zayn.

00:10:11.477 --> 00:10:14.880
du vest vern a pensyoner, un azoy vestu aroysgeyn mit di ZVANye."

00:10:15.814 --> 00:10:19.370
nu, zogt er, "veyst vos? shrayb on a raport

00:10:19.370 --> 00:10:24.530
tsum natshalnik militsye." ⟨geheysn hot er⟩ IVAKHNENKO, mayn natshalnik, a mayor, ⟨K⟩⟨UNK⟩...

00:10:23.847 --> 00:10:25.427
vi ⟨a-⟩ zayn familye iz geven...?

00:10:25.116 --> 00:10:26.560
⟨ma-⟩ IVAKHNENKO.

00:10:26.091 --> 00:10:27.300
IVAKHNENKO.

00:10:27.036 --> 00:10:27.738
 ya.

00:10:30.512 --> 00:10:34.727
er hot mir diktirt, der Mikhlis, vi ikh zol shraybn dem raport.

00:10:34.727 --> 00:10:36.311
kh'hob ongeshribn a raport.

00:10:37.465 --> 00:10:42.690
nu, un ikh bin, kh'hob arayngetrogn dem natshalnik.

00:10:42.865 --> 00:10:46.498
kh'hob im gevizn dem raport. leyent er durkhet far mir in di oygn,

00:10:46.498 --> 00:10:48.820
nemt er tseraysn, varft araynet.

00:10:48.838 --> 00:10:53.680
zogt er tsu mir, "ILI RABOTAT' BUDESH', ILI V TYUR'ME POYDЁSH'!" UNK...

00:10:52.821 --> 00:10:55.127
vos iz dos oyf yidish? "oder du vest..."

00:10:54.762 --> 00:10:57.880
"oder du vest arbetn, oder vest geyn bay mir in turme!"

00:10:58.170 --> 00:10:59.890
⟨azoy hot er mir⟩ geentfert.

00:11:00.313 --> 00:11:03.118
nu, avek a por teg,

00:11:03.118 --> 00:11:05.600
ruft er mir vider arayn, der Mikhlis:

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:09.217
"nu, vi, vi iz di rezultatn?" dertseyl ikh im altseding.

00:11:10.168 --> 00:11:14.957
er hot ober gevust. er zogt, "veyst vos? du bist a shnayder, host in Kovne eltern,

00:11:14.957 --> 00:11:18.090
dayn gantse familye iz in Kovne. do iz far dir keyn ort nit."

00:11:18.623 --> 00:11:22.886
er zogt, "vos er hot tserisn ⟨dem⟩ raport, nem nit in kop. shrayb a tsveytn."

00:11:23.652 --> 00:11:25.654
ongeshribn a tsveytn raport.

00:11:25.896 --> 00:11:30.092
er zogt, "itster, shik dos aveket direkt in Klaypede."

00:11:31.667 --> 00:11:32.938
azoy hob ikh geton:

00:11:32.938 --> 00:11:34.583
avekgeshikt in Klaypede.

00:11:34.583 --> 00:11:39.070
s'iz avek umgefer a tsvey vokhn. kumt on a prikaz UVO- UVO-...

00:11:38.400 --> 00:11:39.676
a bafel, ya?

00:11:39.510 --> 00:11:41.130
a bafel bafrayen fun...

00:11:40.577 --> 00:11:41.735
bafrayen.

00:11:41.130 --> 00:11:42.280
ya. VSЁ.

00:11:42.214 --> 00:11:44.435
dos iz shoyn geven ⟨der⟩ tsvey un fuftsikter yor?

00:11:43.660 --> 00:11:45.870
tsvey un fuftsiktn yor, ya.

00:11:45.589 --> 00:11:48.063
zayt ir gevorn azoy bafrayt fun der milits.

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:48.640
 ya.

00:11:48.357 --> 00:11:49.971
un ir zayt gekumen in Kovne.

00:11:49.473 --> 00:11:50.750
gekumen in Kovne.

00:11:50.483 --> 00:11:53.616
vi hot ir z- vi hot zikh tsuzamengeleygt ayer lebn in Kovne?

00:11:53.571 --> 00:11:58.273
in Kovne... nu, ikh hob dokh khasene gehat in zeks un fertsiktn yor, zayendik in Shilute shoyn.

00:11:58.465 --> 00:12:01.320
dort iz bay mir geborn gevorn Ruvke shoyn.

00:12:01.165 --> 00:12:02.340
ayer zun, ya?

00:12:02.025 --> 00:12:05.020
ya, der elterer zun iz dortn geborn gevorn.

00:12:05.653 --> 00:12:07.824
der lebn iz geven zeyer a shverer dortn.

00:12:08.134 --> 00:12:09.478
ikh fleg bakumen

00:12:09.518 --> 00:12:14.324
zekhtsik, tshervontses, flegt men kenen krign a ⟨tsen⟩⟨UNK⟩ bulbe far derayn.

00:12:14.324 --> 00:12:17.392
zeyer, zeyer shver gelebt dortn in, Shilute.

00:12:18.259 --> 00:12:25.650
nu, zi hot zikh eyn tsayt ⟨ge-⟩ ayngeordnt als, pasportistke.

00:12:26.713 --> 00:12:30.672
nu, ober nokh dem hot zi farshvangert un ⟨hot zikh gemuzt⟩ bafrayen fun der arbet.

00:12:32.012 --> 00:12:33.997
nu, ⟨v- un⟩ vayter,

00:12:34.324 --> 00:12:35.938
mir zaynen gekumen in Kovne.

00:12:36.045 --> 00:12:38.216
gekumen in Kovne, iz nit keyn arbet.

00:12:38.239 --> 00:12:40.983
me hot mir DAZHE nit gevelt tsushraybn in Kovne.

00:12:41.952 --> 00:12:48.403
ikh hob genumen oyfvayzn az ikh bin aleyn a Kovner. kh'hob gearbet in Kovner m-, militsye do un do,

00:12:48.403 --> 00:12:51.200
altseding. hobn zey gezogt,

00:12:51.200 --> 00:12:53.830
hot mir geentfert, der natshalnik funem

00:12:53.899 --> 00:12:56.137
PASPORTNYY STOL,...

00:12:56.802 --> 00:13:00.812
az, "bay undz iz do in Kovne ge-, arbetsloz; me darf nit hobn.

00:13:01.020 --> 00:13:05.440
un oyb m'hot dir bafrayt fun dortn, mistome bistu yener, yener tip geven."

00:13:06.690 --> 00:13:11.679
nu, azoy hob ikh zikh opgemutshet, un nokh dem ⟨hot zikh⟩ ongefangen, Tsherne hot mir zeyer fil geholfn.

00:13:12.715 --> 00:13:14.666
nu, Tsherne hot mir geholfn.

00:13:14.723 --> 00:13:17.884
zey hobn dan gelebt oyf MAIRONIO gas in zeyer a shlekhte dire.

00:13:17.884 --> 00:13:19.391
a dank mir

00:13:19.768 --> 00:13:22.347
hobn zey gebitn di dire oyf GRUODŽIO gas,

00:13:22.347 --> 00:13:23.933
zeyer a gute dire,

00:13:23.933 --> 00:13:25.567
fir tsimern geven dortn.

00:13:25.962 --> 00:13:28.439
dan hot mir di mame avekgegebn a tsimer.

00:13:28.439 --> 00:13:31.979
ikh bin geven UNK, Ruvke iz shoyn geven.

00:13:32.390 --> 00:13:35.186
 dortn hobn mir opgelebt biz

00:13:35.749 --> 00:13:37.278
fir un zekhtsiktn yor.

00:13:38.247 --> 00:13:44.113
nokh dem hot zikh ongefangen, m'hot genumen gebn alemen dires, ale partizaner UNK. nu, hob ikh oykh genumen fodern a dire.

00:13:44.288 --> 00:13:47.319
beshas mayse hot men mir gegebn a tsimer

00:13:47.443 --> 00:13:51.014
oyf DAUKŠOS gas. dortn hot gelebt Srolke Gitlin.

00:13:52.303 --> 00:13:56.617
hot men mir ave- hot men mir gevelt avekgebn zayn tsimer, un im hot men gegebn a naye dire.

00:13:56.944 --> 00:13:58.524
nu, hob ikh zikh antzagt.

00:13:59.408 --> 00:14:02.520
tsu mir iz geven gekumen Dovid Teper

00:14:03.306 --> 00:14:09.951
un nokh eyner. zey hobn bakukt bay mir di, di lage in tsimer. zogn zey, "du host a gants gutn tsimer

00:14:09.951 --> 00:14:12.817
un kenst lebn vayter in dem tsimer."

00:14:14.173 --> 00:14:16.192
nu, hob ikh gezogt tsu Dovid Tepern...

00:14:16.620 --> 00:14:21.560
⟨,⟩ zogt er, "oyb es gefelt dir nit, kenst nokh shraybn a,...

00:14:20.839 --> 00:14:21.896
onklog.

00:14:21.560 --> 00:14:23.735
a onklog tsu, tsu SNIEČKUSn."

00:14:24.535 --> 00:14:28.292
nu, zog ikh, "oybe shraybn, vel ikh bay dir nit, geyn fregn vu tsu shraybn."

00:14:28.332 --> 00:14:30.115
un ver iz dan geven SNIEČKUS?

00:14:30.407 --> 00:14:33.590
der ershter sekretar fun, fun,

00:14:33.647 --> 00:14:35.480
di komunistishe partey in Li- in Lite.

00:14:36.840 --> 00:14:40.250
 nu, nokh dem iz,

00:14:40.250 --> 00:14:42.162
⟨⟩, gebitn di dire,

00:14:42.709 --> 00:14:50.160
un do hot men genumen gebn partizaner alemen dires, hob ikh vider genumen... ⟨un⟩ der glavner iz geven SOLOMIN geven, oyf farteyln dires.

00:14:50.640 --> 00:14:54.680
bin ikh avek tsu im. er iz dan geven der,

00:14:54.707 --> 00:14:58.155
der direktor fun, fun biblyotek iz er dan geven.

00:14:58.155 --> 00:15:02.920
avek tsu im, ikh hob im gegebn dokumentn, ⟨, di⟩ gantse POLOZHENye, un azoy un azoy...

00:15:01.862 --> 00:15:03.324
di gantse lage, yo.

00:15:03.077 --> 00:15:07.140
gantse lage, az mir lebn in eyn tsimer mit a OBSHCHe kikh un alts UNK...

00:15:05.963 --> 00:15:07.543
mit an algemeyne kikh.

00:15:07.273 --> 00:15:08.840
mit a algemeyne kikh.

00:15:08.840 --> 00:15:11.779
nu, un, un ikh hob gefodert a dire.

00:15:12.460 --> 00:15:15.700
⟨nu, iz es⟩ gegangen mir zeyer shver.

00:15:15.852 --> 00:15:18.304
s'iz nito keyn dire, m'hot genumen antzagn.

00:15:18.304 --> 00:15:20.590
m'hot mir shoyn gehat bashtimt tsu gebn a dire,

00:15:20.590 --> 00:15:26.370
bin ikh avek in, in, in, in undzer RAYISPOLKOM.

00:15:25.555 --> 00:15:27.979
oysfir-kom, yo? rayonishn oysfir-ko-...?

00:15:27.020 --> 00:15:28.440
rayonishn ⟨oysfir-kom⟩.

00:15:28.440 --> 00:15:32.450
hobn zey gezogt az itster hot eyner opgebrent a shtub lebn MAISTAS,

00:15:32.450 --> 00:15:35.567
un er iz, er hot nit vu tsu lebn un er ligt oyfn gas un,

00:15:35.567 --> 00:15:40.174
un "du host nokh tsayt; ⟨du⟩ lebst nokh, in a gute, in a gutn tsimer."

00:15:40.174 --> 00:15:41.732
m'hot mir vider nit gegebn.

00:15:42.025 --> 00:15:45.726
nu, ikh ze az s'geyt zeyer shver, hob ikh zikh gevendt tsu Tshernen.

00:15:45.726 --> 00:15:48.448
bay Tshernen flegt kumen Vilenski's froy.

00:15:49.872 --> 00:15:54.810
hot zi ir dertseylt di gantse lage mit mir mit di dire, hot zi dertseylt im.

00:15:55.255 --> 00:15:56.737
hot er gezogt,

00:15:56.737 --> 00:15:58.120
"es meg

00:15:58.512 --> 00:16:01.121
iberkern zikh di velt, du vest krign a dire."

00:16:01.296 --> 00:16:03.300
un er hot mir geshafn di dire.

00:16:03.793 --> 00:16:06.554
un azoy lebt ir in der dire biz der hayntikn tog.

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:11.420
biz hayntikn tog. ot di dire hob ikh bakumen a dank Vilenskin, dem GEROY SOVETSKOGO SOYUZ⟨A⟩...

00:16:10.341 --> 00:16:12.208
dem held fun Ratn-Farband.

00:16:11.669 --> 00:16:13.840
ya. held fun Ratn-Farband.

00:16:13.767 --> 00:16:16.950
un v-, vifl iz geblibn itster ayer mishpokhe?

00:16:18.154 --> 00:16:20.510
vifl mentshn hot ir itster in ayer mishpokhe?

00:16:20.213 --> 00:16:23.464
nu, itster iz de- der zun,

00:16:23.824 --> 00:16:30.480
u- Elke, un der tsveyter zun lebt in Klaypede, Ruvke, mit, mit, mit di froy un di tsvey kinder, tsvey meydlekh.

00:16:30.186 --> 00:16:33.909
un di froy hot ir farlorn, mit, in vifl tsayt ⟨ar-⟩...?

00:16:32.940 --> 00:16:35.330
mit, fir a halb monat tsurik.

00:16:35.333 --> 00:16:36.981
iz geshtorbn ayer froy.

00:16:37.476 --> 00:16:39.174
finf un tsvantsiktn DEKABR'.

00:16:43.703 --> 00:16:45.502
gut. a groysn dank aykh

00:16:45.508 --> 00:16:49.180
far zeyer a sheynem un insha- inhaltsraykhn intervyu.

00:16:51.094 --> 00:16:53.010
tsvey sho hot gedoyert.

00:16:57.895 --> 00:17:01.292
der vos zitst lebn mir, dos iz mayn yingerer zun.

00:17:01.292 --> 00:17:03.220
im ruft men ⟨IL'YA⟩.

00:17:03.940 --> 00:17:06.330
im iz itster zeks un draysik yor.
